These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel, disco, techno
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | gospel | dubstep | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, chinchilla, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | chinchilla | ferret | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, reading, cooking, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | cooking | skydiving | reading | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
